content: I wake up at 7 am and go to bed at 10 pm. I have work from 9 am to 5 pm, and I'd like to set reminders for my lunch break at 12 pm and my morning and evening social media checks. I also want to allocate time for exercise at 7:30 am and focused work from 2 pm to 4 pm. I'm open to using a digital calendar or task management app, whichever you recommend.
